race.comment: NEXT PAY RUN (6) progressive mare who handled the jump in grade with a courageous third over 1400m at Inverell in BM88 class. Has an excellent record on her home track and can bounce back from the good gate. Hard to hold out. CHANGE THE DATE (3) shuffled back from the inside gate and failed to get into the contest with an out-of-character ninth over 1590m at Ballina. Drawn out with the claim and assess on his good win at Taree. Top-three chance. UNDER THE CAP (2) peaked fourth-up with a game victory over 1400m at Deepwater. Meets some better types this time but another big run is on the cards. MONTGOMERY (10) six weeks between runs when back in trip with a fading tenth over 1183m at this track. Showed good early speed last time out and gets out to his preferred trip. Value player.
